@startuml SafeTransfer Local Deployment
title SafeTransfer - Local Deployment

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodeStyle rectangle

node "Developer Machine" as DevMachine {
  artifact "Postman / curl / Swagger UI" as Client
  node "Spring Boot JVM\nSafeTransfer\noptional bootRun" as App
}

node "Docker" as Docker {
  node "safe-transfer-app\nSpring Boot container\noptional full stack" as AppContainer
  database "safe-transfer-postgres\nPostgreSQL" as Postgres
  queue "safe-transfer-kafka\nKafka" as Kafka
  artifact "kcat container\noptional local proof" as Kcat
}

Client --> App : HTTP localhost:8080
Client --> AppContainer : HTTP localhost:8080
App --> Postgres : JDBC localhost:5432
App --> Kafka : Kafka localhost:9092\nwhen Kafka publishing enabled
AppContainer --> Postgres : JDBC postgres:5432
AppContainer --> Kafka : Kafka safe-transfer-kafka:29092
Kcat --> Kafka : safe-transfer-kafka:29092\nDocker network

note right of App
  Host JVM can use:
  .\gradlew.bat bootRun

  Kafka publishing can be enabled with:
  SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE=local
  or APPLICATION_KAFKA_PUBLISHING=true
  and SPRING_KAFKA_BOOTSTRAP_SERVERS=localhost:9092
end note

note right of AppContainer
  Full Docker stack:
  docker compose -f docker/docker-compose-with-app.yml up --build
end note

note right of Kafka
  Local compose exposes:
  localhost:9092 for host app
  safe-transfer-kafka:29092 for Docker clients
end note

@enduml
